description:
Kid in the Cockpit

Aired on 11/09/2005, Narrated by Jonathan Aris.

On 23 March 1994, Aeroflot Flight 593, an Airbus A310-300, is en route to Hong Kong when it stalls and crashes, killing 75 people. The pilot's 15-year-old son accidentally disabled the autopilot.
